{
  "text": "where z a is the standard deviation for tail area a under a Normal distribution. This leads to approximate 2nd, 9th, 25th, 50th, 75th, 91st, and 98th centiles using the two-thirds of a standard deviation spacing proposed by [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "2160314"
